results.description: Walsall qualify for the Leasing.com Trophy second round with a thumping 6-0 win over high-fliers Forest Green Rovers.
results.shortTitle: Walsall hit six to progress in Trophy
results.title: Leasing.com Trophy: Walsall hit six to progress as Colchester win derby with Ipswich

results.description: On a day of late FA Cup drama and a coin toss to decide who gets the linesman, BBC Sport looks at Saturday's best first-round action.
results.shortTitle: What happened in the FA Cup on Saturday?
results.title: FA Cup: Thrilling finishes, a coin toss for the linesman and Ball earns the ball in first round

thumbnail.altText: Fan holds homemade FA Cup trophy

results.title: Walsall 2-2 Darlington: National League North side earn replay

results.description: Watch highlights as sixth-tier Darlington score a 97th minute equaliser against National League Walsall to earn a first round replay in the FA Cup.
results.shortTitle: Watch: Darlington stun Walsall with 97th minute equaliser
results.title: FA Cup: Walsall 2-2 Darlington highlights

results.description: Eoin Doyle scores his 14th goal of the season as Swindon extend their winning run to three matches by beating Walsall.

results.title: Walsall 1-2 Mansfield Town

results.title: Darrell Clarke: Shape up, or go and stack supermarket shelves, says Walsall boss

thumbnail.altText: Former Bristol Rovers boss Darrell Clarke has won five of his 18 games in charge at Walsall

results.description: Oldham make the most of their man advantage as they cruised to a 2-0 win against Walsall.
results.title: Oldham Athletic 2-0 Walsall

results.title: Walsall 1-2 Cheltenham Town

results.title: Walsall 0-3 Salford City

thumbnail.altText: Josh Sheehan of Newport County is challenged by Caolan Lavery of Walsall
